Text: SMART is an open source application designed to help data scientists and research teams efficiently build labeled training datasets for supervised machine learning tasks. Starting a new labelling project in SMART is as easy as pressing the “New Project” button on the SMART landing page. All users have the ability to start their own coding projects, though they may be restricted to modifying or deleting existing projects depending on their user roles.
title: A Very Important Title
Label: happy

Text: Once your project has been created, you are ready to start labeling your data! To begin, you can navigate to any project Annotation page from the Projects Page or to a specific Annotation page by pressing the “Annotate” link on the top navigation bar when on a project Details Page or Admin Dashboard page.
